      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Jeff Dyke, president of Sonic Automotive, told CNBC in a recent interview that he sees new car inventories improving “over the next few months.” That, in turn, will help with tight used vehicle inventories, which will hopefully result in lower prices.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
