            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " continues to harangue automakers, a problem which might not be resolved for some time. GM stopped production of the Chevy Silverado, GMC Sierra, and other full-size trucks in the US and Mexico for a week in July to conserve microprocessors. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
